article_title: Enos Park neighborhood to be focus of hospitals’ effort to improve access

article_metadata.description:
Officials from HSHS St. John's Hospital and Memorial Medical Center said Thursday that they will work together on an as-yet-undetermined project in Springfield's Enos Park neighborhood to improve access to health care services.
“To make a difference, you've got to really focus,” Mitchell Johnson, senior vice president and chief strategy officer for Memorial Health System, told The State Journal-Register.
